{"tid":2430845,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"倡上山下鄉學者 子女送美澳","createTime":"2021-03-03T08:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T09:49:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9b91a928edca5e941f8adaed0bba2597da2203","tid":2430845,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T08:21:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210303/P2WPRICRORGYJJSJWUPCHCFFVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210303%2FP2WPRICRORGYJJSJWUPCHCFFVU%2F&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiulRUXPbyrNnFnNFpNAJjDn8%3D&h=5147f729\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210303%2FP2WPRICRORGYJJSJWUPCHCFFVU%2F&h=9dd15a23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210303/P2WPRICRORGYJJSJWUPCHCFFVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n倡上山下鄉學者 子女送美澳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GhYk7I91ftqsgDXHc9egpeyg4AY=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RL6CHQDYPFDG7PYZ5B2BVY4GGY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGhYk7I91ftqsgDXHc9egpeyg4AY%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRL6CHQDYPFDG7PYZ5B2BVY4GGY.jpg&h=1ca22cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■于鴻君曾發表文章建議啟動「新時期上山下鄉」。<br />\n<br />\n內地親政府學者或官員，常被批評「口裏說愛國，身體最誠實」。繼早前有「反美學者」陳平被揭長居美國後，近日又有曾經呼籲重啟「上山下鄉」的北京學者，被指將自己的子女送往澳洲和美國讀書，網民諷稱其為「陳平第二」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北大黨委管意識形態<br />\n<br />\n于鴻君是北京大學黨委常務副書記，兼任北大馬克思主義學院院長，負責黨建、意識形態、思想政治的工作。他。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n文章當時引起很大迴響，他曾接受訪問時表示，認為文革時期的「上山下鄉」運動利大於弊，十分有益。不過近日他被揭不但沒有將自己的子女送去上山下鄉，反而讓兒子到澳洲留學，女兒則往美國波士頓留學。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上山下鄉運動發生於1950年代至1978年，在文革時期達到高峯，主要是組織城市知識分子和青年到農村定居、勞動和接受教育。中共總書記習近平在1969年亦曾以知青身份，插隊陝西梁家河村七年。<br />\n<br />\n網易"},{"pid":"c6d97f83009edcca282957ea4ea8a7b28a1807d7","tid":2430845,"uid":88737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"匪菜：你又話上山下鄉既？<br />\n支那學者：唔叫你上山下鄉，我邊有錢送d 仔女去美澳呀？"},{"pid":"e9c3a84e660947bb5e0952275e053f09bf78583e","tid":2430845,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:43:05.000Z","msg":"中共總書記習近平在1969年亦曾以知青身份，插隊陝西梁家河村七年。<br />\n<br />\n小學雞都叫知青。"},{"pid":"1f5fbb8d2b88f19bd805cb9eea1715d25af77d01","tid":2430845,"uid":293650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"大陸有千千萬個陳平。"}]}